title: SUPRA Two For Tuesday: Lizard King Bs Lipslide Revert
description:
Two For Tuesday is our new weekly feature dropping every Tuesday on SupraSkateboarding.com and Instagram. It will consist of one trick two angles, one angle regular speed and a slomo, or just two tricks.

Our second installment goes out to this Bs lip revert after dropping down two sets of stairs by Lizard King.

Video By:
Alan Hannon
Dennis Martin
